cold and hot¶

In [17]:
def convert1(data):
    data[data > 0] = 1
    data[data == 0] = 0
In [18]:
basket1 = pd.DataFrame(basket_cold)
array = np.array(basket1)
columns=basket1.columns
index = basket1.index
convert1(array)
cold = pd.DataFrame(array, columns=columns, index=index)
